{"tid":1395891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畫豬頭人諷刺中国人  女漫畫家涉崇日辱华被捕","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:51:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"76df554a76be0bbf1f7c70dff28e5345f4d9a223","tid":1395891,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2416585/190801-01_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2416585%2F190801-01_1024.jpeg&h=1b8836bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地一位年輕女漫畫家近年不時以漫畫諷刺社會現象，先後繪畫300多幅「豬頭人身」畫作，題材包括諷刺中國人在外地惹人側目的不文明行為，惟近日當地公安指她為崇日的「精日分子」，畫作侮辱中國人、傷害中華民族感情，以涉嫌辱華將她拘捕，案件引起中外網民關注。<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體報道，來自安徽的22歲女漫畫家張冬寧，擅長日語曾赴日本，近年以微博帳號「橘豚月月抽」分享自家創作漫畫，題材大多揭示及諷刺社會時弊，包括中國遊客在泰國自助餐廳搶食、乘客在車廂大搗亂、老兵討薪、愛國五毛黨及種種中國人境外不文明行為等，畫作中除外國人外，內地人全為「豬頭人身」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2416585/1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2416585%2F1_600.jpg&h=84f14307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2416585/4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2416585%2F4_600.jpg&h=1c523417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安徽省警方本周日（7月28日）指，已破獲一宗境內外「精日」分子利用互聯網實施「辱華」違法犯罪活動案件，並已逮捕張女。通報中提及的「精日」即「精神日本人」，形容精神上嚮往日本文化、盲目崇拜日本的人士，認為他們厭棄中國人身份、罔顧歷史事實，竭力為日本侵略罪行辯解洗白。<br />\n<br />\n警方認為拘捕行動是阻止張女繼續從事犯罪活動，淨化網絡空間，通報中形容張女的作品侮辱中國人形象，<br />\n<br />\n    「刻意歪曲中國歷史事實，曲解國內外熱點新聞、事件，以諷刺、醜化中國人生活習慣。」<br />\n<br />\n內地同行聲援：藝術創作需自由<br />\n<br />\n事件在國內外引起巨大回響，一位北京漫畫家武文建向公安局發公開信支持張女，形容張女有才氣，並指藝術創作需要自由，漫畫造型或需要誇張，信中提及：<br />\n<br />\n    「艱難的中美貿易戰僵持之際，你們抓捕漫畫小女孩讓外媒跟進，就是給中國領導添亂，此時應該制造民主自由的氣氛，你們倒好，反其道而行之，你們豬頭不豬頭？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2416585/3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2416585%2F3_600.jpg&h=68cadd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2416585/7_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2416585%2F7_600.jpg&h=6bcce6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2416585/6_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2416585%2F6_600.jpg&h=f069aa88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2416585/%E7%95%AB%E8%B1%AC%E9%A0%AD%E4%BA%BA%E8%AB%B7%E5%88%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%86%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E3%80%80%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E6%B6%89%E5%B4%87%E6%97%A5%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9a47c6102acd9ac8a51908518f2e4255300e06a5","tid":1395891,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"解決唔到問題就解決........"},{"pid":"c3d0f10146bd36c028fb3635db9b0289abc6d5d9","tid":1395891,"uid":281417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a0251f1ebee4c2b4b6d2b125eb5137270314cb1","tid":1395891,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾清比人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ead202883fb1b3cc0ed7d4c44a88d874bb9f05","tid":1395891,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"氣質女流"},{"pid